{"tid":1166270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"裁判官吳蕙芳明言：如果報告好，我未必接納；唔好，就即刻坐監！","createTime":"2019-05-22T10:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T01:57:37.000Z","uid":48286,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5514d38f906fe95c5690306dccf3469c53f369","tid":1166270,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n持單程證來港的新移民婦人帶10歲兒子到廣華醫院求診時，不滿等候時間過長，而出手襲擊急症室護士，案件今日（22日）於九龍城裁判法院再提堂，婦人承認1項普通襲擊罪，獲准保釋至6月11日等候社會服務令報告再判刑。主任裁判官吳蕙芳明言：<br />\n<br />\n佢去到救人嘅地方添煩、添亂、撒野，我一定唔會放過！<br />\n<br />\n裁判官決定先為被告索取社會服務令報告再判刑，但明言：<br />\n<br />\n如果報告好，我未必接納；唔好，就即刻坐監！以暴力去打醫護人員，我唔會姑息，唔會放過，我未決定點罰你！<br />\n<br />\n清官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5457c6ef9bc64339b70ef009d874418351f2bde1","tid":1166270,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e670e2a7ac2823dfea1265e807675bfd56f0fccd","tid":1166270,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b6fce209b465c5c3c6eaf1a98ba5a0e92481f7","tid":1166270,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"好官"},{"pid":"2d5c1bb0dbd5a6a310bb4643dd9382445a663d3b","tid":1166270,"uid":154570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4788ebf55269af9764cb1de510afde36e7e7285d","tid":1166270,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed63e30092c8461b869accbae6750bdb47ef160c","tid":1166270,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislik